<DOC><DOCNO>  ZF108-583-566  </DOCNO><DOCID>08 583 566.andM;</DOCID><JOURNAL>MacWEEK  June 26 1990 v4 n24 p13(1)* Full Text COPYRIGHT Coastal Associates Publishing L.P. 1990.andM;</JOURNAL><TITLE>Aldus set to ship PrePrint utility for four-color PageMaker seps.andO;(product announcement)</TITLE><AUTHOR>Said, Carolyn.andM;</AUTHOR><DESCRIPT>Company:   Aldus Corp. (product introduction).andO;Ticker:    ALDC.andO;Product:   PageMaker (Desktop publishing software) (computer programs)PrePrint (Image processing software) (product introduction).andO;Topic:     ColorPrintoutsProduct IntroductionAdd-In-On Software.andM;</DESCRIPT><TEXT>By Carolyn SaidandM;Seattle -- Aldus PageMaker users can produce four-color separations withAldus PrePrint, a $495 separation and color-image editing utility scheduledto ship this week from Aldus Corp.andM;PrePrint separates entire PageMaker files, including text, TIFF andEncapsulated PostScript images.andP;  Users also can edit scanned-in color photoswith PrePrint automatically or manually.andP;  Additionally, PrePrint can softenor sharpen images; improve tonal ranges; enhance highlights, midtones andshadows; adjust lightness, darkness, contrast and saturation levels; andremove dominant color casts.andM;The utility includes a number of built-in options to guide users unfamiliarwith color science, the company said.andM;&quot;[PrePrint] finds and automatically adjusts things that you might not seeunless you were a color person who'd been doing it for 10 years,&quot; saidbeta-user Daniel Clark, vice president of Raging Fingers Inc., a designcompany and service bureau based in Los Angeles.andP;  &quot;Auto-enhance andauto-balance almost guarantee that you're going to get good output.&quot;andM;Clark said he found PrePrint-generated output to be comparable to traditionalseparations &quot;for medium- to good-quality color.andP;  It's not for high-endcolor.&quot;andM;PrePrint provides controls for various types of printing presses.andP;  Inaddition, the program can output four-color separations to a PostScriptimagesetter or print composites for proofing on a PostScript color laserprinter.andP;  Users who prefer to strip in photos can take advantage of theutility's capability to selectively mask all or some TIFF images.andM;Registered owners who bought PageMaker Color Extension before Dec.andP;  31, 1989,will receive PrePrint for free.andP;  Other Color Extensions owners can receive a$100 rebate.andM;Aldus Corp. is located at 411 First Ave.andP;  S., Seattle, Wash.andP;  98104; (206)622-5500.andP;  n</TEXT></DOC>